---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Logo from "@/assets/logos/3.png";
---

<footer class="bg-zinc-400/10 backdrop-blur-lg ring ring-zinc-50/20">
    <div
        class="container pt-8 mx-auto flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-10 text-center lg:flex-row lg:text-left"
    >
        <div
            class="flex w-full max-w-96 shrink flex-col items-center justify-between gap-6 lg:items-start"
        >
            <div>
                <span
                    class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 lg:justify-start"
                >
                    <Image src={Logo} alt="logo" class="size-16" />
                    <p class="text-3xl text-white font-semibold">
                        Dominga Dominguez
                    </p></span
                >
                <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-zinc-400">
                    ¡No te quedes sin vivir la experiencia Dominga Domínguez en
                    nuestro exclusivo tercer piso con vista panorámica!
                </p>
            </div>
            <ul class="flex items-center space-x-6 text-zinc-400">
                <li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                    <a
                        href="https://www.instagram.com/domingadominguez_oficial/"
                        ><svg
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="0"
                            viewBox="0 0 448 512"
                            class="size-6"
                            height="1em"
                            width="1em"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            ><path
                                d="M224.1 141c-63.6 0-114.9 51.3-114.9 114.9s51.3 114.9 114.9 114.9S339 319.5 339 255.9 287.7 141 224.1 141zm0 189.6c-41.1 0-74.7-33.5-74.7-74.7s33.5-74.7 74.7-74.7 74.7 33.5 74.7 74.7-33.6 74.7-74.7 74.7zm146.4-194.3c0 14.9-12 26.8-26.8 26.8-14.9 0-26.8-12-26.8-26.8s12-26.8 26.8-26.8 26.8 12 26.8 26.8zm76.1 27.2c-1.7-35.9-9.9-67.7-36.2-93.9-26.2-26.2-58-34.4-93.9-36.2-37-2.1-147.9-2.1-184.9 0-35.8 1.7-67.6 9.9-93.9 36.1s-34.4 58-36.2 93.9c-2.1 37-2.1 147.9 0 184.9 1.7 35.9 9.9 67.7 36.2 93.9s58 34.4 93.9 36.2c37 2.1 147.9 2.1 184.9 0 35.9-1.7 67.7-9.9 93.9-36.2 26.2-26.2 34.4-58 36.2-93.9 2.1-37 2.1-147.8 0-184.8zM398.8 388c-7.8 19.6-22.9 34.7-42.6 42.6-29.5 11.7-99.5 9-132.1 9s-102.7 2.6-132.1-9c-19.6-7.8-34.7-22.9-42.6-42.6-11.7-29.5-9-99.5-9-132.1s-2.6-102.7 9-132.1c7.8-19.6 22.9-34.7 42.6-42.6 29.5-11.7 99.5-9 132.1-9s102.7-2.6 132.1 9c19.6 7.8 34.7 22.9 42.6 42.6 11.7 29.5 9 99.5 9 132.1s2.7 102.7-9 132.1z"
                            ></path></svg
                        ></a
                    >
                </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                    <a
                        href="https://www.facebook.com/domingadominguezrestaurante?fref=nf&ref=embed_post"
                        ><svg
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            fill="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="0"
                            viewBox="0 0 512 512"
                            class="size-6"
                            height="1em"
                            width="1em"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            ><path
                                d="M504 256C504 119 393 8 256 8S8 119 8 256c0 123.78 90.69 226.38 209.25 245V327.69h-63V256h63v-54.64c0-62.15 37-96.48 93.67-96.48 27.14 0 55.52 4.84 55.52 4.84v61h-31.28c-30.8 0-40.41 19.12-40.41 38.73V256h68.78l-11 71.69h-57.78V501C413.31 482.38 504 379.78 504 256z"
                            ></path></svg
                        ></a
                    >
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div><div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-20">
            <div>
                <h3 class="mb-6 font-bold text-white">Product</h3><ul
                    class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400"
                >
                    <li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Overview</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Pricing</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Marketplace</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Features</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div><div>
                <h3 class="mb-6 font-bold text-white">Company</h3><ul
                    class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400"
                >
                    <li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">About</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Team</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Blog</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Careers</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div><div>
                <h3 class="mb-6 font-bold text-white">Resources</h3><ul
                    class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400"
                >
                    <li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Help</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Sales</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Advertise</a>
                    </li><li class="font-medium hover:text-primary">
                        <a href="#">Privacy</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><div
        class="mt-20 flex flex-col justify-between gap-4 border-t pt-8 text-center text-sm font-medium text-zinc-400 lg:flex-row lg:justify-around pb-8 lg:items-center lg:text-left"
    >
        <p>
            © {new Date().getFullYear()} Dominga Dominguez. Todos los derechos reservados.
        </p><ul class="flex justify-center gap-4 lg:justify-start">
            <li class="hover:text-primary">
                <a href="#"> Termino y condiciones</a>
            </li><li class="hover:text-primary">
                <a href="#"> Politica de privacidad</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</footer>
